## 9. Portal Integration

All apps under:

/portal/apps/

MUST:

* include Tailwind
* follow card layout
* align to grid

Example layout:

<div class="p-4 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <!-- cards -->
</div>

---

## 10. Migration Strategy

Step 1:
Create design system files

Step 2:
Test on ONE app (e.g., observability_hub)

Step 3:
Refactor all apps gradually

Step 4:
Enforce rule in all AI prompts

---

## 11. Validation

A UI is VALID if:

* spacing is consistent
* no inline CSS exists
* all cards visually match
* no random font sizes exist

